scene.message:
Yukino: The "Eternal Night,"{nl}
you say?! Don't mess with us!{waitkey}{clearbox}You called yourself the{nl}
"Night Queen," right? Quit{nl}
hiding and come out! Fight{nl}
us fair and square!!{waitkey}{ret}

Night Queen's Voice: Hmhmhm...{nl}
You too shall become an ice{nl}
statue.{waitkey}{clearbox}Kuroori's Voice: Hihii~ S-{wait_fr:30}stop{nl}
it...{wait_fr:30} gah......{waitkey}{ret}

Night Queen's Voice:{nl}
Ahahaha... Come now, run{nl}
about or you'll freeze solid.{waitkey}{clearbox}Toro's Voice: Waah, stop{nl}
stop stop{wait_fr:30} stop it!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ms. Natsumi's Voice: Hey! Who{nl}
are you{wait_fr:30}?!{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Gyaaaaaah...{wait_fr:30}aagh{wait_fr:30}......{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Nearly everyone in{nl}
the building has been frozen.{waitkey}{clearbox}Before the Queen returns, you{nl}
all must get away, at least...{waitkey}{ret}

Student's Spirit: With the{nl}
last of our remaining power,{nl}
we'll send you outside the{nl}
building.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: For us alone to flee{nl}
with our tails between our{nl}
legs! We can't...{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: She's coming back!{nl}
There's no time!! Now, you{nl}
understand?{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl0f:1}! I'm counting on you{nl}
to look after everyone!!{waitkey}All of you{wait_fr:30}, survive...{waitkey}{ret}
